snippet.title: Metroid Fan Game: Minitroid Demo - Tokinsom
snippet.description:
Check out "Minitroid" an amazing, fan made game based off of the Metroid series, courtesy of user Tokinsom, and enjoy a miniture Metroid adventure!

Thanks to Tokinsom for the video! Check out his YouTube channel at: http://www.youtube.com/Tokinsom

IGN's YouTube is just a taste of our content. Get more:
